descript.abstract: This data set portrays the outline of roads and driveways located on the University of Idaho Campus Moscow, Idaho as of 2005. This is a polygon data set allowing for deriving area values of roadways of campus.
descript.purpose: This dataset is intended for use by Facilities Services for producing maps and managing assets of the University of Idaho. These data are provided to the public primarily for use by University of Idaho students to aid in the completion of course projects. However, these data are not being updated on a regular basis and are current only to 2005. No responsibility is assumed by the University of Idaho in the use of these data.

The original ArcInfo coverage was loaded into an ArcSDE 9.2 Geodatabase. Some attributes from the original dataset were not imported. The dataset was projected from State Plane East NAD27 to State Plane West NAD83 using the NADCON Transformation. Metadata was created.
